'''Toyouke Shrines''' are shrines dedicated to {{ill|Toyouke-Ōmikami|ja|豊受大御神|12=draft|12=draft}}.
* {{ill|Toyouke Shrine (Funabashi)|ja|豊受神社 (船橋市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - A shrine in {{ill|Kanasugi, Funabashi|ja|金杉 (船橋市)|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Funabashi City|ja|船橋市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Chiba Prefecture|ja|千葉県|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Toyouke Shrine (Urayasu)|ja|豊受神社 (浦安市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - A shrine in {{ill|Nekozane, Urayasu|ja|猫実 (浦安市)|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Urayasu City|ja|浦安市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Chiba Prefecture. One of the shrines participating in the {{ill|Urayasu Sansha Festival|ja|浦安三社|12=draft|12=draft}}, held once every four years. [http://members3.jcom.home.ne.jp/urayasusannjya/] * {{ill|Toyouke Shrine (Ichikawa)|ja|豊受神社 (市川市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - A shrine in {{ill|Iseyado, Ichikawa|ja|伊勢宿|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Ichikawa City|ja|市川市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Chiba Prefecture. * {{ill|Toyouke Shrine (Fujioka)|ja|豊受神社 (藤岡市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - A shrine in {{ill|Mitsugi, Fujioka|ja|三ツ木|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Fujioka City|ja|藤岡市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Gunma Prefecture|ja|群馬県|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Toyouke Shrine (Jōsō)|ja|豊受神社 (常総市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - A shrine in {{ill|Misaka Town, Jōsō|ja|三坂町|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Jōsō City|ja|常総市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Ibaraki Prefecture|ja|茨城県|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Toyouke Shrine (Mizuho)|ja|豊受神社 (瑞穂市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - A shrine in {{ill|Nōzu Gekū Higashimachi, Mizuho|ja|生津外宮東町|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Mizuho City|ja|瑞穂市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Gifu Prefecture|ja|岐阜県|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Toyouke Shrine (Chiryū)|ja|豊受神社 (知立市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - A shrine in {{ill|Nagasone Town, Maruyama, Chiryū|ja|長篠町丸山|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Chiryū City|ja|知立市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Aichi Prefecture|ja|愛知県|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Toyouke Shrine (Shikokuchūō)|ja|豊受神社 (四国中央市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - A shrine in {{ill|Toyosaka, Tomisato Town, Shikokuchūō|ja|富郷町豊坂|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Shikokuchūō City|ja|四国中央市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Ehime Prefecture|ja|愛媛県|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Related Pages == * {{ill|Ise Grand Shrine|ja|伊勢神宮|12=draft|12=draft}} - The outer shrine ({{ill|Gekū|ja|外宮|12=draft|12=draft}}) is the {{ill|Toyouke Daijingu|ja|豊受大神宮|1=Toyouke Daijingu|2=ja|3=豊受大神宮|4=zh|5=豐受大神宮|12=draft|12=draft}}, where {{ill|Toyouke-Ōmikami|ja|豊受大御神|12=draft|12=draft}} is the main deity.
